## Why This Is Asked

Tests practical, beginner-friendly design for tenant isolation and latency without overengineering.

## Key Concepts

- Per-tenant read routing
- Replica lag awareness and failover
- Data isolation via schemas or tenant filters
- Caching for hot tenants

## Code Example

